{"tid":554248,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普幕僚：信耶穌可抗流感","createTime":"2018-02-08T10:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T10:39:19.000Z","uid":70985,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa7ee1641742da9f2819643fef6905d8a207c9c","tid":554248,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180208/s00005/8e66fa0fb22458006aa9d90767b0387b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180208%2Fs00005%2F8e66fa0fb22458006aa9d90767b0387b.jpg&h=8b337a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球多地踏入冬季流感高峰期，各地政府都呼籲人們接種疫苗，以防感染。然而，近日美國總統特朗普的宗教顧問，得州牧師寇普蘭（Gloria Copeland）卻公開表示，世上沒有所謂的「流感季節」，更聲言只要堅信耶穌便可抗流感。<br />\n<br />\n寇普蘭指，世上沒有所謂的「流感季節」，呼籲人們不要輕易相信他人有關流感的威脅。她又稱，耶穌已經為人們「注射了疫苗」，而耶穌也犧牲自己，帶走了所有疾病。因此人們只需要堅定信念，不斷和自己說「我不會有流感」，病症便能痊癒。<br />\n<br />\n美國自去年10月起踏入流感季節，據美國疾控預防中心數據表示，自2017年10月1日起至2018年1月27日，全美共有破紀錄的14,676人患上流感住院，是去年全年的兩倍。中心呼籲市民盡快接種流感疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=pvoKMgHca0k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1%26v%3DpvoKMgHca0k&d=dgvwQtRVwxUBrRXODtoMvdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=68b1ef9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=1&amp;v=pvoKMgHca0k</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180208/s00005/1518078431819\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180208%2Fs00005%2F1518078431819&d=dgvwQtRVwxUBrRXODtoMvdZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=23ea15c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180208%2Fs00005%2F1518078431819&h=33af7d8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180208/s00005/1518078431819</a>"},{"pid":"43d345b6ae3cb9deb5158dec8f3c565bcc8b66ba","